          ],
          "text": "RBI/DCM/2016-17/35 Master Direction DCM(CC) No.G -2/03.35.01/2016-17 July 20, 2016",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b2",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.55999755859375,
            209.92799377441406,
            395.19744873046875,
            241.61996459960938
          ],
          "text": "1. The Chairman & Managing Director/Chief Executive Officer (All Banks having Currency Chests)",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b3",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.55999755859375,
            255.64796447753906,
            220.32003784179688,
            287.3399353027344
          ],
          "text": "2. The Director of Treasuries (State Governments)",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b4",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.55999755859375,
            301.2479553222656,
            158.25599670410156,
            317.2199401855469
          ],
          "text": "Dear Sir/Madam",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b5",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.55998992919922,
            329.0639343261719,
            543.4598999023438,
            377.471923828125
          ],
          "text": "Master Direction on Levy of Penal Interest for Delayed Reporting/Wrong Reporting/Non-Reporting of Currency Chest Transactions and Inclusion of Ineligible Amounts in Currency Chest Balances",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b12",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            237.08990478515625,
            360.2225341796875,
            357.62628173828125,
            480.7589111328125
          ],
          "text": "Withdrawn",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 28.0,
            "name": "Arial",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b6",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.55999755859375,
            390.7679443359375,
            543.4598999023438,
            470.21990966796875
          ],
          "text": "In terms of the Preamble, under Section 45 of the RBI Act, 1934 and 35 A of the Banking Regulation Act, 1949, the Bank issues guidelines / instructions for realising the objectives of our Clean Note Policy. With a view to sustain these efforts and ensure discipline among the banks on timely and accurate reporting of currency chest transactions, we have issued instructions on the subject.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b7",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.55999755859375,
            490.8479919433594,
            540.2416381835938,
            538.6199951171875
          ],
          "text": "2. The Master Direction enclosed incorporates updated guidelines / circulars on the subject. The Direction will be updated from time to time as and when fresh instructions are issued.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b8",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.55999755859375,
            559.1279296875,
            465.69598388671875,
            575.0999755859375
          ],
          "text": "3. This Master Direction has been placed on RBI website at www.rbi.org.in.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b9",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.55999755859375,
            600.5279541015625,
            152.97598266601562,
            616.5
          ],
          "text": "Yours faithfully,",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b10",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.55999755859375,
            662.68798828125,
            195.5760040283203,
            694.5
          ],
          "text": "(P. Vijaya Kumar) Chief General Manager",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b11",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.55999755859375,
            710.2079467773438,
            154.2960205078125,
            726.1799926757812
          ],
          "text": "Encl : As above",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        }
      ],
