    {
      "page_number": 2,
      "width": 595.4400024414062,
      "height": 841.6799926757812,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b0",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            503.3999938964844,
            70.9439697265625,
            543.4559936523438,
            87.6719741821289
          ],
          "text": "Annex",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b1",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.55999755859375,
            120.864013671875,
            543.4559936523438,
            151.39199829101562
          ],
          "text": "1. Penal interest for Delayed Reporting/Wrong Reporting/Non-Reporting of Currency Chest Transactions",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b2",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.55999755859375,
            162.5040283203125,
            352.4159851074219,
            179.23202514648438
          ],
          "text": "1.1 Reporting of Currency Chest Transactions",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b3",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.55999755859375,
            190.48805236816406,
            553.535888671875,
            222.18002319335938
          ],
          "text": "The minimum amount of deposit into/withdrawal from currency chest will be Rs.1,00,000/- and thereafter, in multiples of Rs.50,000/-.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b4",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.56002807617188,
            235.94403076171875,
            242.25729370117188,
            252.67202758789062
          ],
          "text": "1.2 Time limit for Reporting",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b5",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.56002807617188,
            263.904052734375,
            543.4585571289062,
            327.5401306152344
          ],
          "text": "1.2.1 The currency chests should invariably report all transactions through ICCOMS on the same day by 9 PM by uploading data through the Secured Website (SWS) to their respective link offices. Link offices should invariably report the consolidated position to the Issue Offices latest by 11 PM on the same day.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b6",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.56002807617188,
            341.42413330078125,
            543.457275390625,
            373.2601318359375
          ],
          "text": "1.2.2 The Sub-Treasury Offices (STOs) should report all transactions directly to the Issue Office of the Reserve Bank by 11 PM on the same day.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b14",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            237.08990478515625,
            360.2225341796875,
            357.62628173828125,
            480.7589111328125
          ],
          "text": "Withdrawn",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 28.0,
            "name": "Arial",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b7",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.56002807617188,
            387.0241394042969,
            369.5760192871094,
            403.75213623046875
          ],
          "text": "1.2.3 Relaxation in respect of strike period in banks",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b8",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            103.56002807617188,
            415.0081481933594,
            543.4573364257812,
            446.82012939453125
          ],
          "text": "Relaxation in the reporting period on account of general/specific strike situation will be considered on case-to-case basis.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b9",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.55999755859375,
            460.5841369628906,
            290.3759765625,
            477.3121337890625
          ],
          "text": "1.3 Levy of penal interest for delays",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b10",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.55996704101562,
            488.42413330078125,
            543.4585571289062,
            599.7001342773438
          ],
          "text": "1.3.1 In the event of delay in reporting currency chest transactions, penal interest at the rate indicated in paragraph 3 of this circular will be levied on the amount due from the chest holding bank for the period of delay. Penal interest will be calculated on T+0 basis i.e. penal interest will be levied in respect of transactions not reported by Link Office to the Issue Office by 11 PM on the same business day. However, Reserve Bank may at its discretion grant appropriate grace period in the matter of levy of penal interest.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b11",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.55996704101562,
            613.5841064453125,
            543.4586181640625,
            645.420166015625
          ],
          "text": "1.3.2 Penal interest will also be charged for delay in submission of chest slips in the case of single chest / STOs directly linked to Issue Department of the circle.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b12",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.55996704101562,
            659.1841430664062,
            348.3359680175781,
            675.9121704101562
          ],
          "text": "1.4 Wrong reporting and levy of penal interest",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b13",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            66.8399658203125,
            687.1680908203125,
            543.4597778320312,
            798.4201049804688
          ],
          "text": "Penal interest will be levied in respect of all cases of wrong reporting in the same manner till the date of receipt of corrected advice by Reserve Bank. As debits/credits to banks' current accounts are raised on the basis of the figures reported in the Link Office Statements, penal interest will invariably be levied in all cases of wrong reporting in the Link Office Statements even if the reporting was done correctly in the chest slips. It is expected that Link Offices would ensure the correctness of figures reported by the respective currency chests. Particular care should be taken to ensure that remittances of",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        }
      ],
      "links": []
    },
    {
      "page_number": 3,
      "width": 595.4400024414062,
      "height": 841.6799926757812,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b0",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            66.83999633789062,
            71.08797454833984,
            543.4583740234375,
            103.3919448852539
          ],
          "text": "fresh notes/notes to the currency chests are not reported as 'deposit' transactions in the Link Office Statements.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b1",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            66.83999633789062,
            116.5439453125,
            538.89599609375,
            133.27194213867188
          ],
          "text": "1.5 Reporting of Soiled note remittances to RBI / diversion to other chests",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b2",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            66.83999633789062,
            146.6879425048828,
            543.457275390625,
            210.17996215820312
          ],
          "text": "Soiled note remittances to RBI /diversion to other currency chest/s should not be shown as withdrawal by chest/s / link offices. In case such remittances are wrongly reported as 'withdrawals', a penalty of Rs.50,000/- will be levied irrespective of the value of remittance and period of such wrong reporting.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b3",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            66.83999633789062,
            223.9439697265625,
            322.89599609375,
            240.67196655273438
          ],
          "text": "1.6 Reporting of diversions in ICCOMS",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b4",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            66.84001159667969,
            254.0879669189453,
            543.4586181640625,
            334.0320739746094
          ],
          "text": "As regards reporting of diversion/s in ICCOMS, they must be reported in the column \"2A and 4 A\" i.e. the chest receiving the diversion should report under 2 A and the remitting chest should report the amount under 4A in the chest slip without any delay. Diversion amounts, even to the chest of the same bank should not be reported under \"Withdrawal\" and \"Deposit\" columns i.e. 4E and 2E (which are for currency transfer transactions).",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b5",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.56002807617188,
            347.0640869140625,
            329.0160217285156,
            363.7920837402344
          ],
          "text": "1.7 Maximum penal interest to be charged",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b11",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            237.08990478515625,
            360.2225341796875,
            357.62628173828125,
            480.7589111328125
          ],
          "text": "Withdrawn",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 28.0,
            "name": "Arial",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b6",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            66.84004211425781,
            375.1680908203125,
            543.4585571289062,
            454.50006103515625
          ],
          "text": "There is no stipulation regarding the maximum amount of penal interest leviable for wrong/delayed reporting. As the intention is to ensure timely and correct reporting of chest transactions, penal interest will be recovered in all applicable cases, irrespective of the amount of the transaction concerned/amount of penal interest subject to rounding off the penal interest amount to the nearest Rupee.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b7",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.56005859375,
            468.2640686035156,
            543.4600219726562,
            498.79205322265625
          ],
          "text": "2. Penal interest for inclusion of ineligible amounts in the currency chest balances",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b8",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.56005859375,
            510.0240478515625,
            543.45849609375,
            605.340087890625
          ],
          "text": "2.1 Penal interest will be levied in all cases where the bank has enjoyed 'ineligible' credit in its current account with Reserve Bank on account of wrong reporting / delayed reporting/non-reporting of transactions. Penal measures will also be taken in cases of shortages in chest balances / remittances, shortages due to pilferage / frauds, counterfeit banknotes detected in chest balances / remittances as per the prevailing \"scheme of Penalties\".",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b9",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.56004333496094,
            619.2240600585938,
            543.4598388671875,
            746.2200927734375
          ],
          "text": "2.2 Further, only cash held in the custody of joint custodians and 'freely available' to them is eligible for inclusion in the chest balances. Thus, cash kept for safe custody in sealed covers for whatever reasons/cash in trunks/bins under the lock and key of any official/s other than the Joint Custodians or bearing a third lock put by any official in addition to the two locks of the Joint Custodians is not eligible for being included in the chest balances. If such amounts are included in the chest balances, these will be treated as instances of wrong reporting and will attract penal interest at the rate specified in para 3.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b10",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.56002807617188,
            760.1040649414062,
            543.4584350585938,
            792.1800537109375
          ],
          "text": "2.3 In all the above cases (excepting shortages in chest balances / remittances, shortages due to pilferage / frauds, counterfeit banknotes detected in chest balances /",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        }
      ],
      "links": []
    },
    {
      "page_number": 4,
      "width": 595.4400024414062,
      "height": 841.6799926757812,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "block_id": "p4_b0",
